Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, Aman Mojadidi on how he uses art to attack the corruption and hypocrisy he sees around him in Afghanistan. And the chance encounter that brought together British writer Julie Wassmer and the daughter she gave up for adoption 20 years earlier. Julie's book is called More Than Just Coincidence. Show less